-- Unipetrol Shares Drop After Czech Refiner Has First-Quarter Loss
-- B y   K r y s t o f   C h a m o n i k o l a s
-- 2012-04-25T08:01:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-25/unipetrol-shares-drop-after-czech-refiner-has-first-quarter-loss.html
Unipetrol AS (UNIP) , the biggest Czech oil
refiner, fell after reporting a first-quarter net loss on
declining sales of motor fuels and rising crude price.  The stock slid 0.7 percent to 170 koruna as of 9:58 a.m. in
Prague, making it the third-worst performer today in the  PX (PX) 
index of 14 companies, which gained 0.9 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Krystof Chamonikolas in Prague at 
